<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Your OTP Code</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #f4f6f8;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .header {
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .header h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .otp-box {
      margin: 30px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .otp {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #007bff;
      letter-spacing: 8px;
    }

    .message {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #aaaaaa;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üîê Project Management App</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="message">
      <p>Dear <strong><%= username %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Use the following OTP to verify your account. The OTP is valid for <strong>5 minutes</strong>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="otp-box">
      <div class="otp"><%= OTP %></div>
    </div>

    <div class="message">
      <p>Please do not share this code with anyone.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Project Management App. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
